{"tid":2462274,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"BCI上海辦：新疆未發現強迫勞動 瑞士總部將會跟隨發表此等聲明","createTime":"2021-03-26T02:01:05.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-26T02:40:13.000Z","uid":21470,"like":6,"dislike":18,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"667ef593e55695fe4543982bea68b243992f3bc3","tid":2462274,"uid":21470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-26T02:01:05.000Z","msg":"「良好棉花發展協會」滬辦指新疆未發現強迫勞動<br />\n<br />\n多間外國企業被指抵制新疆棉花而遭內地官方傳媒批評，被內地傳媒指是幕後推手的「良好棉花發展協會」(BCI)上海代表處回應稱，中國團隊未在新疆發現強迫勞動，企業行為與他們無關。<br />\n<br />\n包括H&amp;M等多間被批評的外國企業都是協會會員。<br />\n<br />\n「良好棉花發展協會」是一個以推動全球棉花業可持續發展的國際非牟利組織，總部在瑞士，在上海也設有辦事處。<br />\n<br />\n協會3月1日在微博的聲明指出，中國項目團隊自2012年起，對新疆進行的驗證，從未發現強迫勞動事件。<br />\n<br />\n但有外國傳媒說，聲明僅代表上海代表處觀點，而協會總部將會發表聲明。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1582688-20210326.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1582688-20210326.htm&d=eMoIgPJs71q5KSiTXOS1Gmipy2YcCk4ac690EPkq9Sw%3D&h=b3f740c2\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1582688-20210326.htm&h=0767e5a7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1582688-20210326.htm</a>"},{"pid":"bdbffcb63a48b5cf2422297e222c25ac0d7914e3","tid":2462274,"uid":1327,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-26T02:03:37.000Z","msg":"跪了"},{"pid":"0f4b28a5d2c9f21badc727b16eae6364fa579b01","tid":2462274,"uid":155095,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-26T02:03:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://megapx-assets.dcard.tw/images/e5f033b3-b369-4b66-8b40-2a37665f1fa1/full.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmegapx-assets.dcard.tw%2Fimages%2Fe5f033b3-b369-4b66-8b40-2a37665f1fa1%2Ffull.jpeg&h=1426683c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://megapx-assets.dcard.tw/images/5a7490ce-c5de-4229-8f46-f8efbed11814/640.webp\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/th